VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bSELECT\s+\*\s+FROM\b
WHEN EXPR MISSING:LIMIT\s+\d+|pagination|rownum|TOP\s+\d+|fetchSize && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects "SELECT * FROM" in SQL queries, which can expose unnecessary or sensitive data in JavaScript applications.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for SQL Query: Unrestricted SELECT *.
